"vod_blurb":"在伦敦，一群精通加密货币的好友意外购入了一套名为“Crypto Horrors”的NFT藏品，藏品中描绘的诡异怪物以 “能带来财富与地位” 为诱饵吸引着他们。很快，藏品的诅咒开始显现，数字世界的怪物冲破屏幕，开始逐一猎杀持有者。他们尝试删除、转售甚至销毁NFT，却发现诅咒与所有权绑定，任何持有行为都会招来致命追杀。恐慌不仅在好友间蔓延，更扩散至网络社区，其他持有者也开始遭遇怪事。他们必须在怪物的围猎中，解开诅咒的真相。","vod_remarks":"更新至HD","vod_pubdate":"","vod_total":0,"vod_serial":"0","vod_tv":"","vod_weekday":"","vod_area":"英国","vod_lang":"英语","vod_year":"2026","vod_version":"","vod_state":"","vod_author":"","vod_jumpurl":"","vod_tpl":"","vod_tpl_play":"","vod_tpl_down":"","vod_isend":0,"vod_lock":0,"vod_level":0,"vod_copyright":0,"vod_points":0,"vod_points_play":0,"vod_points_down":0,"vod_hits":163,"vod_hits_day":711,"vod_hits_week":142,"vod_hits_month":565,"vod_duration":"","vod_up":958,"vod_down":341,"vod_score":"6.0","vod_score_all":3804,"vod_score_num":634,"vod_time":"2026-05-01 11:05:19","vod_time_add":1777604707,"vod_time_hits":0,"vod_time_make":0,"vod_trysee":0,"vod_douban_id":36097303,"vod_douban_score":"0.0","vod_reurl":"","vod_rel_vod":"","vod_rel_art":"","vod_pwd":"","vod_pwd_url":"","vod_pwd_play":"","vod_pwd_play_url":"","vod_pwd_down":"","vod_pwd_down_url":"","vod_content":"在伦敦，一群精通加密货币的好友意外购入了一套名为“Crypto Horrors”的NFT藏品，藏品中描绘的诡异怪物以 “能带来财富与地位” 为诱饵吸引着他们。很快，藏品的诅咒开始显现，数字世界的怪物冲破屏幕，开始逐一猎杀持有者。他们尝试删除、转售甚至销毁NFT，却发现诅咒与所有权绑定，任何持有行为都会招来致命追杀。恐慌不仅在好友间蔓延，更扩散至网络社区，其他持有者也开始遭遇怪事。他们必须在怪物的围猎中，解开诅咒的真相。","vod_play_from":"bfzym3u8","vod_play_server":"","vod_play_note":"","vod_play_url":"HD$https:\/\/v10.baofeng10.com\/video\/kongbucangpin\/d1c16d0effed\/index.m3u8","vod_down_from":"","vod_down_server":"","vod_down_note":"","vod_down_url":"","vod_plot":0,"vod_plot_name":"","vod_plot_detail":"","type_name":"恐怖片"},{"vod_id":142711,"type_id":23,"type_id_1":20,"group_id":0,"vod_name":"家和万死兴","vod_sub":"Home Sweet Home \/ ga-hwa-man-sa-seong","vod_en":"jiahewansixing","vod_status":1,"vod_letter":"J","vod_color":"","vod_tag":"","vod_class":"恐怖","vod_pic":"https:\/\/img.picbf.com\/upload\/vod\/20260501-1\/2ab864ae78a81780b6034579939c8a21.webp","vod_pic_thumb":"","vod_pic